claims:
1. A method for rendering a model of an object, comprising: 
acquiring, in an acquisition space, a reflectance field of the object, the reflectance field including a set of reflectance images of the object and a model of the object, the model including a plurality of points; 
deforming, in an object space, the model to generate a deformed model; 
querying, for each point of the deformed model in the object space, the set of the reflectance images in the acquisition space to obtain reflectance coefficients for each point; and 
shading each point according to the corresponding reflectance coefficients to generate an image of the object corresponding to the deforming.
